{lang-eng}Paapa mrutulmaina mammunu lepenu prematho mammu
Prabhu thone lepenu paraloka padavi paapulakitche
Punaruddhaana shakhtichekalige{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Marana punaruddhaana mandaikyathache
Balaatishayamun pondedamu viswasinchu manalo thana
Shakhti yokka mitileni mahaathyamu thelisikonedamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Sarvaadhi kaaramu adhipatyamula kante shakhti
Prabhutwamu lannitikante anninaamamulalo hetchimpa
Badina yuga yugamulalo melaina naamamuna{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Thana shakhtini bayalu barachutaku erparachukonenu
Bala heenulanu ennikaina vaarini vyardha parachutaku
Neechulaina vaarini erparachu konen.{/lang-eng}

